::KitKat::

She woke up in the CR crying.  She couldn't help but wonder what was 
wrong with her.  She wondered what she could do to end her problem. 
She knew right them she had only two options left to her.  She could 
kill herself, which was out of the question.  She knew she would have 
to be reprogrammed. She looked at her body and saw the damaged.  She 
cried one last time and stepped out of the CR.  She saw Drillbit 
standing there. She looked at him with all the pain in her eyes.  
She let the tears rolled down her cheeks as she looked at him.
"I'm so sorry."
She walked up to him and looked into his eyes.  "I..I think I know 
how to stop the pain." 

She fell to her knees.  She whispered, "I need you to reprogram me."
She looked at the floor and wept.
